                TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts53" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts54">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>winn-u ǧāy hēne, winn-u mā_dri hāyiḏ̣ ʕala Mḥēmid hāyiḏ̣ ʕalē-hum, win-hum gāḏ̣ib, gāḏ̣ib, gāḏ̣ib ǧīb mā_dri il-man aǧ-ǧīb mā_dri il-Barhaw al-Bišše? māmin ḥada qēr Barha al-Bišši hal… </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
