                TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts55" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts56">
                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>winn-u ǧāyīn, m-al-mayyit alle ygūl aḷḷa yirḥam-u, ᵊŠḥāde w Barha ʕAbdaḷḷa. winn-u hū zād rāčib ᵊb-galb al… aǧ-ǧīb, bass al-ᵊwlēd mū ǧāyb-u hā! w čān yiǧi. </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
