                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>ʕaǧal al-wēlād ḏōl il-man? mū-hum wēlād-ne? šnōn ᵊb-ʕagl-ak nyattim ʕiǧyān-na, waḷḷa ʕamm-i Barhaw zād mā yigbal! </ANNOTATION_VALUE>
